{
  "id": "69c8c7426ec6bccc1a101c0a",
  "title": "限定的な承認しか受けていない国",
  "created": 1774765896,
  "updated": 1774770329,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c8c7426ec6bccc1a101c0a",
      "text": "限定的な承認しか受けていない国",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774765896,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d021000000000091c941",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8c8db000000000091c912",
      "text": "略称",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d0bc000000000091c94e",
      "text": "\tOC:  other claimants;  その土地・人を収める政党な政府であることを主張する他の政府",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8c8e4000000000091c914",
      "text": "\tUNm: 国連加盟国 (United Nations' member)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8c918000000000091c915",
      "text": "\tnUNm: 国連非加盟国 (Non-United Nations' member)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8ce9f000000000091c934",
      "text": "\tUNo: 国連オブザーバー (United Nations' observer)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8c8dc000000000091c913",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d026000000000091c94a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d025000000000091c949",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_states_with_limited_recognition",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8ce76000000000091c92f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8c748000000000091c906",
      "text": "少なくとも1つの国連加盟国から承認されていない国連加盟国",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8c7ae000000000091c908",
      "text": "\t中華人民共和国",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d08a000000000091c94d",
      "text": "\t\tOC: 中華民国（nUNm）が中国全土と台湾島の領土を主張。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d130000000000091c94f",
      "text": "\t\t非承認:  中華民国（nUNm）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8c7ed000000000091c909",
      "text": " 韓国",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d14e000000000091c950",
      "text": "  OC: 北朝鮮（UNm）が朝鮮半島全域の領土を主張。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8cb48000000000091c924",
      "text": "  非承認:  北朝鮮（UNm）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8cb46000000000091c922",
      "text": " 北朝鮮",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d1c0000000000091c951",
      "text": " \tOC: 韓国（UNm）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8cb46000000000091c923",
      "text": " \t非承認：韓国（UNm）と日本（UNm）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8cbbf000000000091c926",
      "text": " キプロス",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d1cb000000000091c952",
      "text": " \tOC: 北キプロスが北東部の領有権主張。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d1de000000000091c953",
      "text": " \t非承認: トルコ(UNm)、北キプロス(nUNm)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8c80e000000000091c90e",
      "text": "\tイスラエル",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d227000000000091c954",
      "text": "\t\tOC: ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d227000000000091c955",
      "text": "\t\t\tパレスチナ：ヨルダン川西岸、ガザ地区",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d227000000000091c956",
      "text": "\t\t\tシリア：ゴラン高原",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d227000000000091c957",
      "text": "\t\t\tレバノン：シェバア農場地帯",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8c9d7000000000091c919",
      "text": "\t\t非承認:  29の国連加盟国（主にアラブ諸国やイスラム諸国）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8c9d6000000000091c918",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8ce7b000000000091c930",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8ce90000000000091c933",
      "text": "少なくとも1つの国連加盟国から承認されていない国連オブザーバー国",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8ce89000000000091c932",
      "text": "\tパレスチナ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d2d5000000000091c95b",
      "text": " \tOC:  イスラエル（UNm）はパレスチナが主張する地域を係争地（法的にどの国家にも属さない地域）とみなしている。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d2cd000000000091c959",
      "text": "\t\t非承認： ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d51b000000000091c96d",
      "text": "\t\t\tイスラエル（当事者）、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d4f9000000000091c95c",
      "text": "\t\t\tオーストリア（EU）、ベルギー（EU, NATO）、クロアチア（EU, NATO）、デンマーク（EU, NATO）、エストニア（EU, NATO）、フィンランド（EU, NATO）、ドイツ（EU, G7, G20, NATO）、ギリシャ（EU, NATO）、イタリア（EU, G7, G20, NATO）、ラトビア（EU, NATO）、リヒテンシュタイン（EFTA）、リトアニア（EU, NATO）、オランダ（EU, NATO）、北マケドニア（NATO）、スイス（EFTA）、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d5af000000000091c9b2",
      "text": "\t\t\tアメリカ合衆国（G7, G20, NATO, OAS, 常任理事国）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d584000000000091c9a8",
      "text": "\t\t\t日本（G7, G20, 日米関係）、韓国（G20, 米韓関係）、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d5bb000000000091c9b5",
      "text": "\t\t\tパナマ（OAS）、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d510000000000091c967",
      "text": "\t\t\tフィジー（MISG, PIF）、キリバス（PIF）、マーシャル諸島（PIF）、ミクロネシア（PIF）、ナウル（PIF）、ニュージーランド（PIF）、パラオ（PIF）、サモア（PIF）、ソロモン諸島（PIF）、トンガ（PIF）、ツバル（PIF）、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d579000000000091c9a3",
      "text": "\t\t\tミャンマー（ASEAN）、シンガポール（ASEAN）、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d4fe000000000091c95d",
      "text": "\t\t\tカメルーン（AU, OIC）、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d507000000000091c961",
      "text": "\t\t\tエリトリア（）、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d546000000000091c980",
      "text": "\t\t\tモルドバ（）、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8cf39000000000091c937",
      "text": "\t\t157の国連加盟国とローマ教皇庁、サハラ・アラブ民主共和国（nUNm）に承認されている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8ceb6000000000091c935",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8cfa9000000000091c93a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8cf97000000000091c938",
      "text": "少なくとも1つの国連加盟国から承認されていない国連非加盟国",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8cf9f000000000091c939",
      "text": "\tクック諸島",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8cfc0000000000091c93c",
      "text": "\t\tOC:  ニュージーランド（UNm）と自由連合関係にある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d035000000000091c94b",
      "text": "\tニウエ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d03c000000000091c94c",
      "text": " \tOC:  ニュージーランド（UNm）と自由連合関係にある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8cffb000000000091c93d",
      "text": "\tコソボ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d004000000000091c93e",
      "text": "\t\tOC:  セルビア（UNm）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d016000000000091c93f",
      "text": "\tアブハジア",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d615000000000091c9b6",
      "text": "\t\tOC:  ジョージア（UNm）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d61e000000000091c9b7",
      "text": "\t北キプロス",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d624000000000091c9b8",
      "text": "\t\tOC:  キプロス（UNm）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d628000000000091c9b9",
      "text": "\tサハラ・アラブ民主共和国",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d62e000000000091c9ba",
      "text": "\t\tOC: モロッコ（UNm）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8cfb9000000000091c93b",
      "text": " ソマリランド",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d645000000000091c9bc",
      "text": " \tOC:  ソマリア（UNm）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d690000000000091c9bd",
      "text": " 南オセチア",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d69b000000000091c9be",
      "text": " \tOC:  ジョージア（UNm）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d6a2000000000091c9bf",
      "text": " 中華民国",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d6ad000000000091c9c0",
      "text": " \tOC:  中華人民共和国（UNm）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d6b6000000000091c9c1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d6c5000000000091c9c2",
      "text": "他の国連非加盟国によってのみ承認されている国連非加盟国",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d6e3000000000091c9c3",
      "text": " 沿ドニエストル共和国",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d6e8000000000091c9c4",
      "text": " \tOC: モルドバ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d6ef000000000091c9c5",
      "text": " \t承認：アブハジア（nUNm）、南オセチア（nUNm）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8d644000000000091c9bb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774770329,
      "updated": 1774770329
    }
  ]
}